metadata.name: SMPLFRKS #1
metadata.description:
8400 simple alien freaks are ready to take over the Ethereum blockchain.  Packed with day 1 IRL utility giving you IRL savings on all your favorite activities and things.  

Join the selfcare odyssey of a boy named Marvin Stench going way beyond the stars to find his cat and manage life's many obstacles.  Family owned with a mental health focus & foundation rooted in an anti-bullying kids book published in 2017.  Bad times don't last, but SMPLFRKS do.
